  "title": "Mouthwatering Juicy Mexican Tomatoes Tlayudas",
  "description": "A tangy and juicy Mexican dish featuring tomatoes and pickle, served on a crispy tlayuda, perfect for a energizing lunch. This shojin-friendly recipe is made in a paella pan.",
