  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees.",
    "Place the tlayudas in the paella pan and toast in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the cherry tomatoes, pickle, red onion, and cilantro.",
    "Squeeze the lime juice over the tomato mixture and toss to coat.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the olive oil, salt, and pepper.",
    "Brush the olive oil mixture over the toasted tlayudas.",
    "Spoon the tomato mixture over the tlayudas.",
    "Return the paella pan to the oven and bake for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and serve immediately."
  ],
